INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2015-04-27 23:02:47','2015-04-27 23:02:47','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2015-04-27 23:02:47','2015-04-27 23:02:47','',0,'http://htwe.wpengine.com/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2015-04-27 23:02:47','2015-04-27 23:02:47','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://htwe.wpengine.com/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2015-04-27 23:02:47','2015-04-27 23:02:47','',0,'http://htwe.wpengine.com/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(3,2,'2015-07-08 06:46:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2015-07-08 06:46:59','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://htwe.wpengine.com/?p=3',0,'post','',0),(4,2,'2015-07-08 06:50:08','2015-07-08 06:50:08','High Tea with Elephants is a vision inspired by the African safari industry offering you a selection of curated content from across Southern and East Africa.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Home','','publish','open','open','','home','','','2015-07-08 10:38:11','2015-07-08 10:38:11','',0,'http://htwe.wpengine.com/?page_id=4',0,'page','',0),(5,2,'2015-07-08 06:56:43','2015-07-08 06:56:43','','36 Basson Glenvista Pool view-2','','inherit','open','open','','36-basson-glenvista-pool-view-2','','','2015-07-08 06:56:43','2015-07-08 06:56:43','',4,'http://htwe.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/36-Basson-Glenvista-Pool-view-2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(6,2,'2015-07-08 07:07:14','2015-07-08 07:07:14','<h2>Africa, the birthplace of the safari.</h2>\r\n\r\n<b>High </b><b>Tea with </b><b>Elephants</b> is a vision inspired by the African safari industry, where authentic safari experiences, products and stories are showcased and treasured; where we, as safari lovers, are able to celebrate adventures, beauty and creativity with those who share our passion.\r\n\r\nThe launch of this online content platform and e-commerce site is the realisation of founder Christie Fynn Morgan’s dream to have a collective space that encompasses ‘the art of safari’.\r\n\r\nThe team is made up of industry professionals and safari experts with over 35 years of combined experience in the African safari industry. They have a extensive knowledge base of safari lodges all over Southern and East Africa. They are lodge managers, safari guides, travel planners and marketing managers – but at the heart of it they are bush lovers, adventurers, spirited Africans and curators of beautiful African things.','About','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2015-07-08 07:18:13','2015-07-08 07:18:13','',0,'http://htwe.wpengine.com/?page_id=6',0,'page','',0),(7,2,'2015-07-08 07:07:36','2015-07-08 07:07:36','<b>- SHOP WITH US -</b>\r\n\r\nA curated selection of fine art, photography and accessories inspired by Africa.','Shop','','publish','open','closed','','shop','','','2015-07-08 09:22:35','2015-07-08 09:22:35','',0,'http://htwe.wpengine.com/?page_id=7',0,'page','',0),(8,2,'2015-07-08 07:07:52','2015-07-08 07:07:52','Advertise with <strong>High Tea With Elephants (HTWE)</strong> and reach a large, rapidly-expanding community of East and Southern Africa travellers and safari enthusiasts. This exciting new platform offers your business the opportunity to advertise products or destinations and engage with an audience who are passionate about safaris and appreciate all aspects of the industry.\r\n\r\nTo find out more about who we are and how we can work together, please email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@highteawithelephants.com.\">info@highteawithelephants.com</a>\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"#\">DOWNLOAD OUR INFO &amp; ADVERTISING PACK</a></strong>\r\n\r\n<b>EDITORIAL MISSION</b>\r\n\r\n<b>HTWE</b> inspires readers to explore and celebrate the African safari industry. Our passionate, emotive, take on the safari industry delivers a diverse range of curated content which is aspirational and accessible, encouraging readers to cultivate not just a personal connection with the continent but a desire to travel to its wonderful places and spaces and purchase curated items in our Boutique and Gallery.\r\n\r\n<b>BRAND</b>\r\n\r\n<b>HTWE</b> is the insider\'s safari guide with a global outlook, delivering safari style, travel and online shopping in a beautifully designed digital space. HTWE inspires people to experience an African safari by showcasing quality safari-related content that is both beautiful and creative.\r\n\r\n<b>CONTENT</b>\r\n\r\nOur website features a diverse range of quality content, that aims to inspire all world travellers who use the internet to research and book travel in Africa.\r\n\r\n<u><b>THEMES</b></u>\r\n\r\nART | DESIGN AND DECOR | EVENTS | FASHION &amp; ACCESSORIES | FOOD | LITERATURE | LODGES PHOTOGRAPHY | PEOPLE | TRAVEL\r\n\r\n| TRENDS | TIPS &amp; ADVICE | WEDDINGS | WILDLIFE\r\n\r\n<u><b>COUNTRIES</b></u>\r\n\r\nBOTSWANA | BURUNDI | KENYA |NAMIBIA | MALAWI | MOZAMBIQUE | RWANDA\r\n\r\nSOUTH AFRICA | SWAZILAND | TANZANIA | UGANDA | ZAMBIA | ZIMBABWE\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Adv